{"tid":1516002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【繼續清算】警方今再拘捕5名示威者  涉非法集結及襲警罪等","createTime":"2019-08-29T11:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:42:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d713ddd1321fb1bc4592fc0f76df3c60fdd1ff00","tid":1516002,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"反對《逃犯條例》修訂運動再有示威者被捕，<span style=\"color: red;\">本月13日及14日</span>於香港國際機場非法集結，警方經調查後，今日（29日）上午分別在觀塘區及旺角區再拘捕兩名男子，其中一名35歲姓呂男子涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢，另一名30歲姓邱男子則涉嫌非法集結及襲警。兩人現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n另外，3名年齡介乎20至30歲男子，在屯門區及香港仔被捕，警方指，他們今年<span style=\"color: red;\">6月21日和26日</span>參與包圍灣仔警察總部，涉嫌刑事毀壞，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2440038/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2440038%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=163ef64f\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2440038/</a>"},{"pid":"fa5329fbeb36a3acb045a81f49a988249de2be4a","tid":1516002,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"吊你老味 罪行任屈<br />\n班藍絲 黑社會乜事都無"},{"pid":"152a7ec39e08da0d50c948ee46b60c13b7245346","tid":1516002,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"斬人果d又唔見你咁快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07edc67e46624e6f67fb9586c1c97a95ec52fa2","tid":1516002,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612f11acea8fcf99ef9b8af3cfc6fa243a3d58c3","tid":1516002,"uid":93962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:43:17.000Z","msg":"w"},{"pid":"a4b21e29edb490022b4e1a6e5060bc052b43c5c7","tid":1516002,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"946b66232c8b708732d847e1f